		<table class="table">
			<tr>
				<th>Title of Invention</th>
				<td><h1 style="font-size:large;">PRODUCING AN ANTIIRE AN ORGANIC CHEMICAL FORMULATION THAT IS DERIVED FROM BIOLOGICAL SOURCES AND HAVING APPLICATIONS IN THE FIELDS OF INDUSTRIAL / COMMERICIAL AND HOUSEHOLD FIRE-PROOFING, FIRE-RESISTANCE, AND IMPARTING FIRE RESISTING PROPERTIES TO NORMALLY FLAMMABLE MATERIALS, BOTH LIVING &amp; NON-LIVING</h1></td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<th>Abstract</th>
				<td>57) Abstract:- This invention pertains to a herbal non CFC generating, environment friendly inexpensive fire extinguisher cum fire resistant liquid. Conventional fire extinguishers are not herbal and therefore cause some environmental damage and they are also costly. Further, there is no fire extinguisher which can impart fire or bum resistance to normally flammable object such as paper cloth wood and plastic material, etc, in addition to human/animal body parts/skin. In this invention a liquid herbal extract is presented which can extinguish fire and also impart fire/burn resistance to normally flammable objects as paper, cloth, wood and plastic material in addition to human/animal body parts/skin. PRICE: THIRTY RUPEES</td>
			</tr>
		</table>

